The family of Joseph Otieno Olweny, a GSU officer who has been missing for the last month is agonising over his continued absence. The officer who manned the armoury at the general service unit (GSU) Ruaraka barracks disappeared without a trace on the 9th of July and his phone signal was last traced at the gate of the Ruaraka barracks. The car Olweny was using was found in Mwiki. Our reporter Fred Kagonye tells the mysterious disappearance of the officer